  - Creation=Man's Primordial Birthright
  - Union-Identity=Realization And Identity=Know Thyself
By: Plotinus
---
Being is desirable because it is identical with Beauty, and Beauty is loved
because it is Being. ... We ourselves possess Beauty when we are true to our
own being; ugliness is in going over to another order; knowing ourselves, we
are beautiful; in self-ignorance, we are ugly.
